To perform automatic wallet sweep <https://docs.sync.global/validator_operator/validator_helm.html#configuring-sweeps-and-auto-accepts-of-transfer-offers> (on docker compose environment). The ENV variables that need to be set are (on the validator service env variables section):
```      - |
        ADDITIONAL_CONFIG_WALLET_SWEEP=
            canton.validator-apps.validator_backend.wallet-sweep {
              <senderPartyHint::key> {
                max-balance-usd = <amount>
                min-balance-usd = <amount>
                receiver = <receiverPartyHint::key>
                use-transfer-preapproval = true
              }
            }```
